<doc id="466903" wikidata="Q2803916" url="?curid=466903" title="Rhincodontidae">
<text>Rhincodontidae is a shark family which includes the whale shark, the sole extant member and the largest living fish. A single extinct genus, &quot;Palaeorhincodon&quot;, is known from the Paleocene as well.

