* Michel S. Beaulieu, &quot;Labour at the Lakehead: Ethnicity, Socialism, and Politics, 1900-1935.&quot; Vancouver: UBC Press, 2011.
* Michel S. Beaulieu, “The Lakehead and Canada&#x27;s First Social Democratic Party: The Search for Socialist Unity.&quot; Thunder Bay Historical Museum Society &quot;Papers &amp; Records&quot; 39 (2011): 29-54.
* C.H. Cahan, &quot;Socialistic Propaganda in Canada: Its Purposes, Results and Remedies.&quot; Toronto, ON: OISE, 1918.
* Ian McKay, &quot;Rebels, Reds, Radicals: Rethinking Canada&#x27;s Left History.&quot; Toronto: Between the Lines, 2005.

