*Ronald Clements, &quot;In Japan the Crickets Cry&quot; Monarch Publications, 2010. (eyewitness account of Weihsien Camp survivor, Stephen A. Metcalf)
*Duncan Hamilton, &quot;For the Glory&quot; Doubleday, 2016. 
*Eric Eichinger, &quot;The Final Race&quot; Tyndale House, 2018. 
